               java.lang.String naturalAnalog,
               java.lang.String alternateId)
Create a new monomer.

Parameters:
polymerType - : unique text ID for the monomer, will be used in polymer notation
monomerType - : monomer type, Backbone, Branch, UnDefined
naturalAnalog - : the ID of its closest natural analog
alternateId - : unique text ID for the monomer, will be used in polymer notation
